---
title: BBQ Meatloaf & Loaded Potato Wedges Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: Hard to find one option that pleases everyone? Introducing our chef-curated “perfect plates,” where everyone can build their own meal. This one stars juicy meatloaves with crispy potato wedges and roasted broccoli. Serve it all family style with scallions, sour cream, and tangy-sweet BBQ sauce so everyone can choose their own toppings and dippers!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67a9c9ca4113630c74a3454a-578b9ebd.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67a9c9ca4113630c74a3454a-en-US.pdf
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 960 kcal
  fat: 51 g
  saturated fat: 21 g
